snippet.title: Hot Dog King Intro
snippet.description:
Set out to dominate the fast food industry city by city using a mix of talented staff members, the mob, and shady tactics in each franchise to lure customers in.

Hot Dog King is a strategy simulation game with a fresh approach to fast food. You will set out to dominate the fast food industry city by city, using talented staff members in each franchise as your secret weapon to lure customers away from the competition. Play in your own style -- start and develop your business using superior marketing techniques and great food, or build your empire quickly by employing the mob and using shady tactics against your competition.
Genre: Strategy 
Publisher: Meridian4
Developer: Fuzzyeyes Studio
Release Date: April 09, 2007
MSRP: $19.99
Exclusively on: PC
T for Teen
